runtimeAttrs.SQL Query:
SELECT DISTINCT 
    source, 
    companydesc, 
    lobdesc, 
    riskstate, 
    a.annual_statement_line, 
    stateline, 
    directwrittenpremium, 
    cededwrittenpremium, 
    directunearnedpremium, 
    cededunearnedpremium, 
    directlosspaid, 
    directcasereserve, 
    directlossibnrreserve, 
    cededlosspaid, 
    cededcasereserve, 
    cededlossibnrreserve, 
    directpaiddcc, 
    directpaidao, 
    directlaecasreserve, 
    directlaeibnrreserve, 
    cededpaiddcc, 
    cededpaidao, 
    cededlaecasreserve, 
    cededlaeibnrreserve, 
    directcommissionsincurred, 
    cededcommissionsincurred, 
    account_entered_dt, 
    CASE 
        WHEN LENGTH(TRIM(reinsurancecompany)) = 3 THEN CONCAT('0', TRIM(reinsurancecompany)) 
        ELSE TRIM(reinsurancecompany) 
    END AS reinsurancecompany 
FROM ( 
    SELECT 
        'GW_Ceded_Premiums' AS source, 
        p."company desc" AS companydesc, 
        CASE 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = '1' THEN 'Fire' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = '2' THEN 'Extended Coverage (EC)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd IN ('A', '4', '6', '7') THEN 'Homeowner (HO)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = '9' THEN 'Inland Marine (IM)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = 'X' AND COALESCE(p."lob desc", 'Not Applicable') = 'PersonalUmbrella' THEN 'Personal Umbrella (PUMB)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = 'X' AND COALESCE(p."lob desc", 'Not Applicable') = 'CommercialUmbrella' THEN 'Commercial Umbrella (CUMB)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd IN ('81', '82', 'D', 'C') THEN 'Business Owners Policy (BOP)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd IN ('E', '5') THEN 'Commercial Multi Peril (CMP)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = 'Y' THEN 'Dwelling Liability' 
        END AS lobdesc, 
        COALESCE(p."risk state", 'Not Applicable') AS riskstate, 
        f.annualstatementlinecd AS annual_statement_line, 
        f.statelinecd AS stateline, 
        NULL AS directwrittenpremium, 
        SUM(f.mtdwrittenpremiumamt) AS cededwrittenpremium, 
        NULL AS directunearnedpremium, 
        SUM(f.unearnedamt) AS cededunearnedpremium, 
        NULL AS directlosspaid, 
        NULL AS directcasereserve, 
        NULL AS directlossibnrreserve, 
        NULL AS cededlosspaid, 
        NULL AS cededcasereserve, 
        SUM(f.unearnedamt * ref.ibnr_factor) AS cededlossibnrreserve, 
        NULL AS directpaiddcc, 
        NULL AS directpaidao, 
        NULL AS directlaecasreserve, 
        NULL AS directlaeibnrreserve, 
        NULL AS cededpaiddcc, 
        NULL AS cededpaidao, 
        NULL AS cededlaecasreserve, 
        NULL AS cededlaeibnrreserve, 
        NULL AS directcommissionsincurred, 
        SUM(f.mtdwrittencommissionamt) AS cededcommissionsincurred, 
        f.accountentereddt AS account_entered_dt, 
        f.reinsurercode AS reinsurancecompany 
    FROM dbo.policyreinsuranceearnedpremiumfact f 
    LEFT JOIN dbo.view_policy p ON p."part policy key" = f.policykey 
    LEFT JOIN dbo.profitloss_factors_ref ref ON ref.state_line_code = f.statelinecd 
        AND ref.year = CASE 
            WHEN EXTRACT(YEAR FROM f.accountentereddt) <= 2019 THEN 2019 
            ELSE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM f.accountentereddt) 
        END 
    GROUP BY 
        p."company desc", 
        p."risk state", 
        CASE 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = '1' THEN 'Fire' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = '2' THEN 'Extended Coverage (EC)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd IN ('A', '4', '6', '7') THEN 'Homeowner (HO)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = '9' THEN 'Inland Marine (IM)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = 'X' AND COALESCE(p."lob desc", 'Not Applicable') = 'PersonalUmbrella' THEN 'Personal Umbrella (PUMB)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = 'X' AND COALESCE(p."lob desc", 'Not Applicable') = 'CommercialUmbrella' THEN 'Commercial Umbrella (CUMB)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd IN ('81', '82', 'D', 'C') THEN 'Business Owners Policy (BOP)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd IN ('E', '5') THEN 'Commercial Multi Peril (CMP)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = 'Y' THEN 'Dwelling Liability' 
        END, 
        f.accountentereddt, 
        f.annualstatementlinecd, 
        f.statelinecd, 
        f.reinsurercode 
    UNION 
    SELECT 
        'GW_Ceded_Loss' AS source, 
        p."company desc" AS companydesc, 
        CASE 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = '1' THEN 'Fire' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = '2' THEN 'Extended Coverage (EC)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd IN ('A', '4', '6', '7') THEN 'Homeowner (HO)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = '9' THEN 'Inland Marine (IM)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = 'X' AND COALESCE(p."lob desc", 'Not Applicable') = 'PersonalUmbrella' THEN 'Personal Umbrella (PUMB)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = 'X' AND COALESCE(p."lob desc", 'Not Applicable') = 'CommercialUmbrella' THEN 'Commercial Umbrella (CUMB)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd IN ('81', '82', 'D', 'C') THEN 'Business Owners Policy (BOP)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd IN ('E', '5') THEN 'Commercial Multi Peril (CMP)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = 'Y' THEN 'Dwelling Liability' 
        END AS lobdesc, 
        COALESCE(p."risk state", 'Not Applicable') AS riskstate, 
        f.annualstatementlinecd AS annual_statement_line, 
        f.statelinecd AS stateline, 
        NULL AS directwrittenpremium, 
        NULL AS cededwrittenpremium, 
        NULL AS directunearnedpremium, 
        NULL AS cededunearnedpremium, 
        NULL AS directlosspaid, 
        NULL AS directcasereserve, 
        NULL AS directlossibnrreserve, 
        SUM(CASE WHEN f.reservecd = 'Indemnity' THEN f.paidamt END) AS cededlosspaid, 
        SUM(CASE WHEN f.reservecd = 'Indemnity' THEN f.reservechangeamt END) AS cededcasereserve, 
        NULL AS cededlossibnrreserve, 
        NULL AS directpaiddcc, 
        0 AS directpaidao, 
        NULL AS directlaecasreserve, 
        NULL AS directlaeibnrreserve, 
        SUM(CASE WHEN f.reservecd = 'Defense' THEN f.paidamt END) AS cededpaiddcc, 
        SUM(CASE WHEN f.reservecd = 'Adjustment' THEN f.paidamt END) AS cededpaidao, 
        SUM(CASE WHEN f.reservecd = 'Indemnity' THEN f.reservechangeamt * ref.lae_case_factor END) AS cededlaecasreserve, 
        SUM(CASE WHEN f.reservecd = 'Indemnity' THEN f.reservechangeamt * ref.lae_case_factor * ref.lae_ibnr_factor ELSE 0 END) AS cededlaeibnrreserve, 
        NULL AS directcommissionsincurred, 
        NULL AS cededcommissionsincurred, 
        DATE_TRUNC('month', f.adddt) AS account_entered_dt, 
        f.reinsurancecode AS reinsurancecompany 
    FROM dbo.claimreinsurancetransaction f 
    LEFT JOIN dbo.view_policy p ON p."part policy key" = f.policykey 
    LEFT JOIN dbo.profitloss_factors_ref ref ON ref.state_line_code = f.statelinecd 
        AND ref.year = CASE 
            WHEN EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATE_TRUNC('month', f.accountentereddt)) <= 2019 THEN 2019 
            ELSE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATE_TRUNC('month', f.accountentereddt)) 
        END
        where
		f.accountentereddt <= date_trunc('month', current_date)
    GROUP BY 
        p."company desc", 
        p."risk state", 
        CASE 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = '1' THEN 'Fire' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = '2' THEN 'Extended Coverage (EC)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd IN ('A', '4', '6', '7') THEN 'Homeowner (HO)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = '9' THEN 'Inland Marine (IM)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = 'X' AND COALESCE(p."lob desc", 'Not Applicable') = 'PersonalUmbrella' THEN 'Personal Umbrella (PUMB)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = 'X' AND COALESCE(p."lob desc", 'Not Applicable') = 'CommercialUmbrella' THEN 'Commercial Umbrella (CUMB)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd IN ('81', '82', 'D', 'C') THEN 'Business Owners Policy (BOP)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd IN ('E', '5') THEN 'Commercial Multi Peril (CMP)' 
            WHEN f.statelinecd = 'Y' THEN 'Dwelling Liability' 
        END, 
        DATE_TRUNC('month', f.adddt), 
        COALESCE(p."risk state", 'Not Applicable'), 
        f.annualstatementlinecd, 
        f.statelinecd, 
        f.reinsurancecode 
) a 
ORDER BY a.account_entered_dt, source
